OL,3,CFather murdered by two teenage boys in
OL,4,C'unprovoked racist attack'
OL,6,FTwo teenage boys have been sentenced
OL,7,Ffor murdering a father who died after
OL,8,Fbeing stabbed in the heart during an
OL,9,Funprovoked racist attack.
OL,11,FMarcus Staniforth, 17, and a 16-year-
OL,12,Fold boy who cannot be named for legal
OL,13,Freasons, approached Kamran Aman, 38,
OL,14,Fafter he dropped groceries at his
OL,15,Fmother's home in Barry, Vale of
OL,16,FGlamorgan.
OL,18,FThe pair punched and kicked Mr Aman,
OL,19,Fwith the 16-year-old shouting racist
OL,20,Fabuse during and after the attack.
