OL,6,FStaniforth fetched a kitchen knife
OL,7,Ffrom a nearby property, where the
OL,8,Fteenagers had been drinking alcohol,
OL,9,Fand used it to stab Mr Aman in the
OL,10,Fheart.
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,13,Fscene but Mr Aman, who was married and
OL,14,Fhad a young child, was pronounced dead
OL,15,Fat 1.07am on July 1, 2025.
