OL,6,FMr Justice Griffiths told Cardiff
OL,7,FCrown Court that he had lifted
OL,8,Freporting restrictions relating to
OL,9,FStaniforth, meaning he can now be
OL,10,Fidentified, but added that those
OL,11,Frelating to the 16-year-old boy would
OL,12,Fremain in place.
OL,14,FThe judge sentenced both defendants to
OL,15,Fdetention during His Majesty's
OL,16,FPleasure, with Staniforth to serve a
OL,17,Fminimum of 17 years in custody and the
OL,18,F16-year-old boy to serve a minimum of
OL,19,F15 years.
