OL,4,C'unprovoked racist attack'
OL,6,FMr Justice Griffiths described how the
OL,7,F16-year-old had painted "where they
OL,8,Fn****** at" on the wall of a house
OL,9,Fwhere he had been.
OL,11,FThe boy, who had taken cocaine, later
OL,12,Fspotted Mr Aman through a window as he
OL,13,Fsat in his car.
OL,15,F"He noticed he was not white," the
OL,16,Fjudge said. "Mr Aman caught his eye
OL,17,Fbecause he was black."
