OL,6,FThe 16-year-old boy then tried to open
OL,7,FMr Aman's car door, with Mr Aman
OL,8,Fgetting out of the vehicle before
OL,9,Fbeing punched.
OL,11,F"He wanted to hurt him really badly
OL,12,Fbecause he was not white ` that was
OL,13,Fhis only reason," the judge said. "He
OL,14,Fwas shouting racist abuse at him,
OL,15,Fcalling him n-word and p-word, over
OL,16,Fand over again."
OL,18,FThe judge added that Staniforth was
OL,19,F"not racist but he was violent" and
OL,20,Fwanted to back the 16-year-old in the
OL,21,Fattack.
