OL,6,FSentencing the 16-year-old, the judge
OL,7,Ftold him: "You instigated a
OL,8,Fdeliberate, unprovoked, sustained,
OL,9,Fviolent, racist attack.
OL,11,F"You were old enough and mature enough
OL,12,Fto know that trying to cause a
OL,13,Fcomplete stranger really serious
OL,14,Finjury because of his race was wrong,
OL,15,Fand you knew exactly what you were
OL,16,Fdoing."
OL,18,FProsecuting, Owen Edwards KC told the
OL,19,Fcourt that Mr Aman was stabbed while
OL,20,Foutside his mother's house in an
OL,21,F"entirely unprovoked attack".
