OL,6,FHe said the defendants had been
OL,7,Fdrinking alcohol on June 30, with the
OL,8,F16-year-old behaving in a "volatile
OL,9,Fand aggressive manner" throughout the
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,12,FMr Aman had been working then saw his
OL,13,Fwife and young child before taking
OL,14,Fshopping to his mother on the night of
OL,15,FJune 30.
OL,17,FThe 16-year-old boy noticed Mr Aman
OL,18,Fsitting in his car and "lost his
OL,19,Ftemper", with Staniforth telling him
OL,20,Fhe would "back him up", Mr Edwards
OL,21,Fsaid.
