OL,6,F"Both young men entered the street and
OL,7,Fthe 16-year-old launched a sustained
OL,8,Fassault against Kamran, consisting of
OL,9,Frepeated punches," he told the court.
OL,11,F"Marcus joined in a limited extent,
OL,12,Fwith punches and one hard kick."
OL,14,FMr Edwards said Staniforth then
OL,15,Freturned to a nearby property before
OL,16,Femerging with a large kitchen knife,
OL,17,Fwhich he used to stab Mr Aman.
